# # RFA-U-Net 4-Panel Boundary Visualization
# Plots: Original ⇨ Ground-Truth ⇨ Predicted ⇨ Boundaries (GT=red, Pred=yellow)

# %%
# 1) cd into your repo (uncomment in Colab)
